WEBVTT

00:07.001 --> 00:10.770
Now she never even plays with him.

00:10.838 --> 00:13.239
She never plays with anything.

00:13.306 --> 00:16.452
I'm afraid that your daughter's
increasing lack of affect

00:16.520 --> 00:18.881
is all part of her ongoing
withdrawal from the world.

00:18.939 --> 00:20.340
I don't know what that means--

00:20.407 --> 00:21.744
"withdrawal from the world."

00:25.088 --> 00:27.228
Is she going through
some kind of depression?

00:27.296 --> 00:29.128
Can a 12-year-old even be depressed?

00:29.196 --> 00:32.301
Doctor, I need someone to tell me
what's going on with my daughter.

00:32.369 --> 00:36.496
Your daughter's having delusions,
hallucinations.

00:36.564 --> 00:38.391
She's displaying something

00:38.459 --> 00:40.520
that we call "disorganized speech."

00:40.588 --> 00:42.618
And while I'm not about to diagnosis her

00:42.685 --> 00:44.015
from across the room,

00:44.083 --> 00:46.813
I will tell you that these
are all classic symptoms

00:46.881 --> 00:50.045
of early onset paranoid schizophrenia.

00:52.346 --> 00:54.847
Schizophrenia?

00:54.915 --> 00:58.784
It's clear to me that she's very, very sick.

00:58.851 --> 01:00.817
I'm sorry, you're just wrong.

01:00.885 --> 01:02.352
She's not sick.

01:02.420 --> 01:04.019
She's just going through something.

01:09.227 --> 01:10.660
Oh, God.

01:10.728 --> 01:12.362
Summer, what have you done?!

01:12.430 --> 01:14.492
He wouldn't stop talking to me.

